<!--pages/api/request/form-request/get/get.wxml-->
<view class='container'>
  <view class='content'>
    <view class='title'>向右滑动可查看多本书籍资料</view>
    <swiper class='book-list'>
      <block wx:for="bookList" wx:index="idx">
        <swiper-item class='book'>
          <image class='logo' src='http://img3m2.ddimg.cn/51/34/25159812-1_l_9.jpg' mode='aspectFit'></image>
          <view class='name'>书名：一禅小和尚</view>
          <view class='desc'>幅幅萌到爆棚！独特的水墨彩绘，可爱到喷血的人物形象，真挚的情感共鸣，暖萌减压的诚意之作~ 微博每条漫画转发量平均三万+的国民IP作品，人民日报等主流媒体都纷纷转发的“忒可爱了”作品。</view>
          <view class='toolbar'>
            <image src='../../../../images/add.png' bindtap='add'></image>
            <image src='../../../../images/delete.png' bindtap='delete' data-id="{{item.bookId}}"></image>
            <image src='../../../../images/modify.png' bindtap='modify' data-id="{{item.bookId}}"></image>
          </view>
        </swiper-item>
      </block>
    </swiper>
  </view>
</view>